todoyu loginpage extension changelog

loginpage 1.1.4 - not released yet
	* Added: CapsLock detection + warning
	* Added: Real names of demo-account persons
	* Added: Hook "loginpage.relogin.onreloginresponse"
	* Changed: Style of login-links to buttons to be easier recognized as clickable

loginpage 1.1.3 - 2011-11-17
	* Translation: Polish


loginpage 1.1.2 - 2011-09-15
	* Added: Hooks: login, login.failed


loginpage 1.1.1 - 2011-07-25
	* Bugfix: Login status icon styling fixed (icon was cropped)


loginpage 1.1.0 - 2011-06-17
	* Changed: Requires core 2.1
	* Changed: Structure for 2.1
	* Changed: All classes are prefixed with extension name


loginpage 1.0.6
	* Bugfix: Removed whitespace after password in email body to prevent copy/paste problems
	* Bugfix: Fixed label key: forgotpassword.mail.tologin